ZH: 祸害是一种不好的事情。
EN: Misfortune is something undesirable.
ZH: 恶劣天气对农作物造成了很大的祸害。
EN: Severe weather has caused great damage to crops.
ZH: 科技发展可以带来便利，但也会带来一些祸害。
EN: Technological advancement can bring convenience, but it can also bring some harm.
ZH: 那场火灾对整个城市带来了巨大的祸害。
EN: That fire brought tremendous disaster to the entire city.
ZH: 人类的贪婪和破坏行为给地球带来了巨大的祸害。
EN: Human greed and destructive behavior have brought great harm to the Earth.
ZH: 他的盗窃行为给他自己和家人带来了祸害。
EN: His theft brought harm to himself and his family.
ZH: 污染空气会对人们的健康造成祸害。
EN: Air pollution can cause harm to people's health.
ZH: 激烈的竞争对企业来说可能是一种祸害。
EN: Intense competition can be a harm to businesses.
ZH: 青少年犯罪给社会带来了严重的祸害。
EN: Teenage crime has brought serious harm to society.
ZH: 心灵的黑暗带来的祸害可能比物质的破坏更严重。
EN: The harm caused by the darkness of the soul may be more severe than material destruction.
ZH: 这种病毒对人类健康构成了巨大的祸害。
EN: This virus poses a great harm to human health.
ZH: 贪污和腐败是社会秩序的祸害。
EN: Corruption and bribery are the harms to social order.
ZH: 祸害是我们应该努力避免的东西。
EN: Harm is something we should strive to avoid.
ZH: 那个人的欺骗行为给许多人带来了祸害。
EN: That person's deceitful behavior caused harm to many people.
ZH: 恶意传播谣言会给社会带来祸害。
EN: Maliciously spreading rumors can bring harm to society.
ZH: 不要让你的贪婪给自己带来祸害。
EN: Don't let your greed bring harm to yourself.
ZH: 祸害来临时我们必须采取积极的应对措施。
EN: When harm comes, we must take proactive measures.
ZH: 敌人的侵略给我们的国家带来了无尽的祸害。
EN: The enemy's invasion has brought endless harm to our country.
ZH: 那次意外给她的生活带来了一场祸害。
EN: That accident brought a disaster to her life.
ZH: 毒品滥用对个人和社会都带来很大的祸害。
EN: Drug abuse brings great harm to individuals and society.
